---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ABOUT US | ACHI Studio" description="Discover the minimalist design philosophy and sustainable sourcing values of ACHI.">
  <!-- Top Banner / Editorial Quote -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 border-b border-stone-200/60 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6">
      <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-gold font-semibold mb-3 block">Est. 2026</span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl tracking-widest text-brand-charcoal uppercase leading-tight mb-6">
        CHIC MINIMALISM
      </h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm max-w-[600px] mx-auto tracking-widest font-light text-stone-500 uppercase leading-relaxed">
        Stripping away the excess to reveal the essence of premium materials and timeless silhouettes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left Column: Manifesto -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium pb-2 border-b border-stone-200/80">
          THE MANIFESTO
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
          At ACHI, we believe that true style does not shout; it whispers. We do not design for seasons; we design for longevity. Our garments are constructed to stand the test of time, both in durability and aesthetic relevance.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
          We reject the hyper-cycles of fast fashion. Instead, we advocate for a curated capsule wardrobe—pieces that integrate seamlessly, wear beautifully, and bring calm functionality to everyday life.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Sourcing & Slogan -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium pb-2 border-b border-stone-200/80">
          SUSTAINABLE SOURCING
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Every fabric is audits for environmental trace. We source organic cotton, certified European linen, and recycled polyester blends. Our partnerships are restricted to suppliers who share our dedication to fair labor and minimal waste.
        </p>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-gold pl-6 py-1 italic font-serif text-brand-charcoal text-base">
          "Minimalist High-Quality - That's the Way We Do Business."
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
